title: Brightwood - Wake (2008) [mp3]
description:
Brightwood is a four-piece aggressive melodic rock group based in the Portland, OR area. Their sound is best described as a modern blend of raw, yet intelligent, melodic rock laced with soaring guitars, and passionate vocals. Their sound embodies each of the members individual tastes without adhering to the formula of a particular genre. The result is a brand of music that is undeniably unique and intensely flavorful to the ear.
